<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2370] Access to internal data structures for delayed and service factory components not thread safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2370</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The DelayedComponentManager (supporting delayed components) and ServiceFactoryComponentManager (supporting service factory components) internall keep track of using bundles in a Set or Map. Access to this Set or Map is not synchronize which may cause data structure corruption and operation failures.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12465710">FELIX-2370</key>
            <summary>Access to internal data structures for delayed and service factory components not thread safe</summary>
